values:
A lot of people have asked if they should keep this journal on their list, and some want to keep it on to go back and look at old pictures,
but I've deleted all my friends, so that you won't have an inactive name on your list (because i think it's annoying)  and I will probably
post some of my old photos in my new journal if people want to see them.



i also decided not to delete the journal in case I ever wanted to use it again, so it will just be sitting here. 


anyway, last chance....
